Paper: hep-th/9405074

Date: 1994-05-11

Title: Twistor--like Formulation of D=10, type IIA, Superstrings $^*$

Authors: P.Pasti and M.Tonin

Comments: 22 pages,tex, DFPD/94/TH/05

The twistor--like formulation of the type IIA superstring $\sigma$--model inD=10 is obtained by performing a dimensional reduction of the recently proposedtwistor--like action of the supermembrane in D=11. The superstring action isinvariant under local, worldsheet $(n,n)$ supersymmetry where $3\leq n \leq 8$and is classical equivalent to the standard Green--Schwarz action (at least for$n=8)$